node.text: Healthy, happy mouths, but make it fashion. I’m so excited to partner with my absolute favorite oral care brand @burstoralcare in support of PRIDE and the LGBT Not only is their brush the secret to my white teeth, it now comes with a custom BURST floss designed by yours truly and one of our incredible masks. Grab your #BURSTxCHRISTIANSIRIANO exclusive bundle now at the link in my bio @csiriano and BURST will donate $25K of the proceeds to @trevorproject  #brushburst
